Issues with Job Abandonment/Communication Most clients become irritated when stars fail to keep them updated on the status of their campaigns. To avoid misconceptions, you must be diligent in speaking with them. If there is a disagreement about the quality of campaign, explain politely that you will be unable to do it and contact customer service right away so they can assist them right away. Do not wait several hours to remedy the problem.
2) Client’s Reason for Refund: Plagiarized Document

Save a copy of a plagiarism checker result of the output you have submitted to the client to assure that it is original campaign. Do not forge the result and provide the evidence for the whole document.
3) Client’s Reason for Refund: Did not meet the deadline.

Getting campaigns completed within the provided timeline is the reason for hiring stars. You need to submit the output ahead of time. If the application is having issues, reach out to the customer support via email at support@nojom.co and request them to send the files directly to the client.
4) Client’s Reason for Refund: Not satisfied with the Quality of the Campaign.

Campaigns are not just undertaken with the goal of completing the output before the deadline. You should also deliver a high-quality output result. It is critical to establish a standard for the document you are creating and ensure that it fits the standards. To avoid misconceptions, you must be proactive in asking questions of the client. Because the majority of your clients are still students, you must carefully question them about the directions and the topics you are working with.

Take note that you are responsible for the outcomes you send. While performing their duty, it is your responsibility to address the client\'s issues. If you have any difficulties, ambiguities, or problems, please contact customer service at https://24task.com/contact-us
